Sara Malakul Lane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sara_Malakul_Lane 0 Sara Malakul Lane (Thai: ซาร่า มาลากุล เลน; born 1 February 1983) is a Guam-born English-Thai actress and supermodel that appeared in numerous movies across Thailand and America. She most notably featured in the Kickboxer action film franchise across several films as the main female lead.
